# Environment and Gradle

## First-time setup (Arch Linux script)

Installs JDK, Android SDK, emulator, Node.js; creates **Pixel7** AVD (API 36.1 x86_64 Google APIs). Requires **KVM** (VT-x / AMD-V).

```bash
./setup-env.sh
```

## Common commands

```bash
gradle assembleDebug
gradle assembleRelease
gradle lint
gradle test
gradle clean
```

If Gradle cannot write `~/.android`, use **`ANDROID_USER_HOME=<project>/.android-user`** (see **`build-deploy.mdc`**).
